~ character_1
The abyss listens before it answers. Carry this echo with care.
=> END

~ character_2
Some threads remember the shape of light, even down here.
=> END

~ character_3
The deeper path opens only for those who gather what remains.
=> END

~ character_4
A small pulse returns to you. The silence is not empty.
=> END
